<h3>Instructions</h3>
  <hr />
    <h4>Create account</h4>
    <p>To join Personal DJ, log in by clicking the "Sign in" button. This will take you to a Facebook authentication page. Personal DJ is linked to Facebook in order for you to share your music with friends.</p>
  <br/>
  <h4>Listing & Sharing music</h4>
  <p>Once you have joined us you will be able to list and share music. We use a three step paradigm. Create, share and vote. Firstly you'll need to list your music in a music list. This is a list specific for a club (create). Once you have listed your song you will need to promote it (share). If that has been done, and your song has enough votes to make it to the final list then this list will be availbe in the club (promote).</p>
  <br/>
  <h4>News Feed</h4>
  <p>Here will live posts of clubs been displayed you are following. Artist news, and more.</p>
